{"tid":2178953,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，係”Zhina”唔係”Chi na”啊屌","createTime":"2020-08-28T18:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T04:15:38.000Z","uid":371001,"like":44,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd173bba21741dc007126ff43f84d6101725e75","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:38:57.000Z","msg":"未有account之前成日見到你哋咁打<br />\n冇用㗎，要激嬲支那要打Zhina先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有啲無謂嘅執著但係如果同佢哋罵戰打Chi na<br />\n佢哋會覺得有少少唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係普拼嚟不過整碎到佢哋玻璃心真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Fucking Zhinese spreading virus everywhere~~&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Wait what you from Zhina? Then why are you out here?&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Omg another Zhinese leaving Zhina to steal technology&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Go back to your Weibo Zhinese, YouTube is for human.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過有樣嘢想講<br />\n試過幾次被Zhinese話我被西方Brainwashed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我唔需要同佢哋理性討論<br />\n淨係覆佢&rdquo;A locked up fucked up Zhinese saying people outside the wall being brainwashed? How sarcastic&rdquo;<br />\n已經夠曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorly41999因為而家咁多嘢發生好多負面情緒<br />\n只係分享下我點樣發洩壓力啫<br />\n對住佢哋發洩完之後特別爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好畀位佢哋攻擊或者中佢哋嘅伏<br />\n對住支那口交要有特別嘅技巧<br />\n記得等對方爆粗先好搶道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數會用殘體爆粗<br />\n到時可以用英文翻譯畀外國人睇佢哋幾低賤(如果YouTube comment section)<br />\n<br />\n如果想我分享多啲經驗/戰術我得閒可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時發覺啲支那英文又幾好，學到啲新嘅生字下次罵戰又可以用<br />\n其實想英文進步，罵戰都係一個唔錯嘅選擇<br />\nSorly again41999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b4e67ec03ce8a84b16530e23a79c37e1554236","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:49:05.000Z","msg":"[quote]未有account之前成日見到你哋咁打<br />\n冇用㗎，要激嬲支那要打Zhina先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有啲無謂嘅執著但係如果同佢哋罵戰打Chi na<br />\n佢哋會覺得有<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">小小</span></span>唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係普拼嚟不過整碎到佢哋玻璃心真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a9ffc96abc7f562adf1d7c322d5a1f41ae4fb0","tid":2178953,"uid":359022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"zhina zhinese 細楷啱佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通話拼音先係正統方言 用咩英文"},{"pid":"f3ec3ea0d7b5a9baa05e10096f0547508e93e036","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26a9ffc96abc7f562adf1d7c322d5a1f41ae4fb0","tid":2178953,"uid":359022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"zhina zhinese 細楷啱佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通話拼音先係正統方言 用咩英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:13:39.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過<br />\n等佢哋見到自己幾咁卑賤"},{"pid":"e470b92c090ad3d8419ddf130acad7f2c6576b69","tid":2178953,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3ec3ea0d7b5a9baa05e10096f0547508e93e036","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26a9ffc96abc7f562adf1d7c322d5a1f41ae4fb0","tid":2178953,"uid":359022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:00:07.000Z","msg":"zhina zhinese 細楷啱佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />普通話拼音先係正統方言 用咩英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:13:39.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過<br />\n等佢哋見到自己幾咁卑賤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T19:17:19.000Z","msg