=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSOURCE：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/支那人#當代\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%94%AF%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%BA%23%E7%95%B6%E4%BB%A3&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9dd238ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/支那人#當代</a>"},{"pid":"57c81f60e3b67fa86667efdcf318470b1fcf08b7","tid":2178953,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09923a5743d145ad00d531085ab36335c99899a8","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"96e74f6d8dab9ab14b9f9b3a94dcd927d7f1f0be","tid":2178953,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3321f652fcb962cdb7257ce563a36f2e68f7850","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"我自己account用得好哋哋<br />\n唔需要喇多謝<br />\n我account係大學個email<br />\n連仔應該check到<br />\n唔想被你哋搞到冇咗<br />\n放過我啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"你係唔係pr 大家同連狗心中有數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"成班人冇端端追擊我<br />\n一定會羊群心理整到我account死咗囉<br />\n我有講啲pr會講嘅嘢咩<br />\n我自己打我想打嘅嘢<br />\n點解要被你哋限制我嘅言論自由<br />\n點解要同我戴上帽子呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"唔使咁緊張，都話你係唔係大家心中有數"},{"pid":"e1c8a4c594c9dc59dd548ba15ff649da38801327","tid":2178953,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7967da9705356d89e5a9fbaaad99cd3be270dcfc","tid":2178953,"uid":84668,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d1eed97ab17293fa0bb38b8dd18037691b5b7e60","tid":2178953,"uid":320919,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:09:25.000Z","msg":"支那係當年日本人改嘅名黎<br />\n羅馬拼音 chi na <br />\nカタカナ：チナ<br />\nChing 唔好衝出黎柒啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:16:43.000Z","msg":"你先唔好衝出黎柒啦<br />\n真係唔撚識架喎<br />\n首先，支那日文既羅馬拼音係SHI NA<b